data.description:
5 BED, 4 BATH, 2 Story Home w/ Finished Basement located in Castle Highlands!! Tucked into a quiet cul-de-sac! Tons of Natural light! Remodeled Kitchen-New Refrigerator, Microwave, Dishwasher, Center island, Corian countertops, Abundant cabinets, Hardwood Floors, Pantry and Sunny breakfast nook!  Large Family Room w/ Gas fireplace, Vaulted Ceiling...Open Concept for entertaining!
Main Floor Laundry! Office could be 6th Bedroom! Primary Bedroom w/ large 5-piece ensuite bathroom, large walk-in closet...3 more bedrooms that share a full bathroom w/double sinks! Fully Finished Basement, Huge Recreation - Great room - Game Room w/built-in Entertainment center, Bar, Bedroom and Full bathroom & Extra storage space!! Low Maintenance  Backyard, Pergola, Mature Landscaping! Nestled against the Foothills/Mountains - Open space, trails, and playground at Castle Highlands Park! Near Red Hawk Ridge Golf Course! Endless options...Biking trails, Hiking trails-Ridgeline Trail & Open Space! Just minutes to Castle Rocks historic downtown, Offers shopping, dining & more!! Almost 4400 S.F. of Finished space! Views! Must See!
